value.0: Doorway from the Rainbow Bridge North to the Mirror Maze South.
A searing shaft of blue light descends from some unseen place above.

When you peer into the mirror, rather than a reflection, you can make out some other location through a swirling mist. 

When you reach out to touch it, your hand hits the hard surface of the glass. Maybe this mirror is only a destination from whatever place you see in the mists.

Welcome!

You are nearing the Electric Castle. The fortress lies across the Rainbow Bridge.

Are you brave enough?
